enigma_edit.lua.data

Class CodeSnippet

  • java.lang.Object
    • enigma_edit.lua.data.CodeSnippet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<CodeSnippet>

    public final class CodeSnippet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<CodeSnippet>
    Lua source code location. Essentially this stores position information about a part of a string. For normal processing, the start- and end-character positions are stored. To provide human readable information and line extraction, line- and column- values are also stored for the start- and end-position.

        Create a code snippet from start- and end-position in the code. Line- and column-numbers will be calculated by inspecting the code given.
        Parameters:
        code - Code this snippet is referencing.
        startPos - Start position (as character offset).
        endPos - End position (as character offset).

      • CodeSnippet

        public CodeSnippet(java.lang.String code,
                   int startLine,
                   int startColumn,
                   int endLine,
                   int endColumn)
        Create a code snippet from line/column pairs given for start- and end-position. The real character offsets will be calculated by inspecting the given code string.
        Parameters:
        code - Code this snippet is referencing.
        startLine - Line number of the start position.
        startColumn - Column number of the start position.
        endLine - Line number of the end position.
        endColumn - Column number of the end position.

      • change

        public java.lang.String change(java.lang.String code,
                               java.lang.String replacement)
        Replace the part of code defined by this snippet with a given string. Note, that this operation invalidates every code snippet, that ends after the start position of this snippet. You must take care to update those, if you want to keep using them with the updated code string.
        Parameters:
        code - Source code this snippet is part of.
        replacement - String to replace the part of code defined by this snippet.
        Returns:
        Updated code string.
